 is accidentally deleted.  -->\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* Six Alabama State Senators: [[Clay Scofield]],<ref name=\"marcoala\">{{cite web|url=http://www.alreporter.com/rubio-campaign-announces-alabama-leadership-team/|title=Rubio Campaign Announces Alabama Leadership Team|work=Alabama Political Reporter|date=January 28, 2016}}</ref> [[Slade Blackwell]],<ref name=\"marcoala\"/> [[Greg Albritton]],<ref name=\"marcoala\"/> [[Greg Reed]] (Majority Leader),<ref name=\"mrbama\">{{cite web|url=http://www.al.com/news/index.ssf/2016/02/rubio_endorsed_by_24_alabama_s.html|title=Rubio endorsed by 31 Alabama state elected officials|work=The Birmingham News|date=February 25, 2016}}</ref> [[Steve Livingston]],<ref name=\"mrbama\"/> [[J. T. Waggoner]]<ref name=\"mrbama\"/>\n* Twenty-six Alabama State Representatives: [[Will Ainsworth]],<ref name=\"marcoal\"/> [[Randall Shedd]],<ref name=\"marcoala\"/> [[Danny Garrett]],<ref name=\"marcoala\"/> [[David Faulkner (politician)|David Faulkner]],<ref name=\"marcoala\"/> [[Jack W. Williams (politician)|Jack Williams]],<ref name=\"marcoala\"/> [[Jim Patterson (Alabama politician)|Jim Patterson]],<ref name=\"marcoala\"/> [[K. L. Brown]],<ref name=\"marcoala\"/> [[Kyle South]],<ref name=\"marcoala\"/> [[Mack Butler]],<ref name=\"marcoala\"/> [[Matt Fridy]],<ref name=\"marcoala\"/> [[Mike Jones, Jr.]],<ref name=\"marcoala\"/> [[Nathaniel Ledbetter]],<ref name=\"marcoala\"/> [[Lynn Greer (politician)|Lynn Greer]],<ref name=\"marcoala\"/> [[Mike Ball]],<ref name=\"mrbama\"/> [[Paul Beckman]],<ref name=\"mrbama\"/> [[Chris Blackshear]],<ref name=\"mrbama\"/> [[DuWayne Bridges Sr.]],<ref name=\"mrbama\"/> [[Terri Collins]],<ref name=\"mrbama\"/> [[Danny Crawford (Alabama politician)|Danny Crawford]],<ref name=\"mrbama\"/> [[Jim Hill (Alabama politician)|Jim Hill]],<ref name=\"mrbama\"/> [[Mike Hill (Alabama politician)|Mike Hill]],<ref name=\"mrbama\"/> [[Jimmy Martin (politician)|Jimmy Martin]],<ref name=\"mrbama\"/> [[Bill Poole (politi