y Volk]],<ref name=\"marcomaine\"/> [[Ronald F. Collins]],<ref name=\"marcome\">{{cite web|url=https://marcorubio.com/news/maine-leaders-endorse-rubio/|title=Conservative Mainers Rally Behind Marco|date=March 3, 2016|access-date=March 28, 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160317114354/https://marcorubio.com/news/maine-leaders-endorse-rubio/|archive-date=March 17, 2016|url-status=dead}}</ref> [[Brian Langley]]<ref name=\"marcome\"/>\n* Eighteen Maine State Representatives:  [[Kenneth Fredette]] (Minority Leader),<ref>{{cite web|url=http://stateandcapitol.bangordailynews.com/2015/07/23/ken-fredette-named-maine-campaign-chairman-for-marco-rubio/ |title= Ken Fredette named Maine campaign chairman for Marco Rubio |publisher=bangordailynews |date=2015-07-23}}</ref> [[Robert Nutting (politician)|Robert Nutting]] (former Speaker),<ref name=\"marcomaine\"/> [[Joshua Tardy]] (former Minority Leader),<ref name=\"marcomaine\"/> [[Bruce Bickford (politician)|Bruce Bickford]],<ref name=\"marcome\"/> [[Jim Donnelly (politician)|Jim Donnelly]] (former Minority Leader),<ref name=\"marcome\"/> [[Anthony Edgecomb]],<ref name=\"marcome\"/> [[Robert Foley (American politician)|Robert Foley]],<ref name=\"marcome\"/> [[Karen Gerrish]],<ref name=\"marcome\"/> [[Phyllis Ginzler]],<ref name=\"marcome\"/> [[Matthew Harrington]],<ref name=\"marcome\"/> [[L. Gary Knight]] (former),<ref name=\"marcome\"/> [[Joyce Maker]],<ref name=\"marcome\"/> [[Richard Malaby]],<ref name=\"marcome\"/> [[Dwayne Prescott]],<ref name=\"marcome\"/> [[William Tuell]],<ref name=\"marcome\"/> [[Karen Vachon]],<ref name=\"marcome\"/> [[Nathan Wadsworth]],<ref name=\"marcome\"/> [[Dustin White]]<ref name=\"marcome\"/>\n* Maryland State Senator: [[Justin Ready]]<ref name=\"marcomary\">{{cite web|url=http://www.p2016.org/rubio/rubio020916prmd.html|title=Rubio Campaign Files for Maryland Ballot with Full Slate of Delegates|work=p2016.org|date=February 9, 2016}}</ref>\n* Eight Maryland State Delegates: [[Chris